      "$value": "Plus Jakarta Sans",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "Sole typeface across the product. Geometric humanist sans with subtly squared terminals — contemporary but not cold. Weight 700 carries display and headings for confident vertical presence; weight 500 serves UI controls and labels; weight 400 handles body and descriptions. The slight openness in counters at small sizes keeps labels legible on dense tool surfaces."
